{"tid":2009161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立法會35+目標係咩？","createTime":"2020-05-09T14:08:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T07:26:22.000Z","uid":37957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8bac3c692e8ff518772f9a8c1a93e00de159461d","tid":2009161,"uid":37957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T14:08:15.000Z","msg":"我一直都以為立法會35+就係為咗攞到否決權去投反對票攬炒，而要達到35+就要靠初選避免浪費票。<br />\n即係初選嘅目的就係希望最終攞到否決權攬炒<br />\n<br />\n但最近有啲自稱唔係泛粉/議助嘅會員同我講，唔支持攬炒都可以參加初選<br />\n<br />\n如果立法會35+唔係為咗否決議案攬炒，有冇人可以同我講，而家爭取立會35+係為咩？"},{"pid":"bf3adcaf234a739a309aa701a0d7a469012af371","tid":2009161,"uid":64922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T14:17:27.000Z","msg":"過左35個唔駛講議案住<br />\n首先第一步大口狗個位就係民主派<br />\n主席個位已經可以玩殘港共<br />\n過35所有事務委員會正負又係包晒<br />\n基本唔撚駛玩咩否決權攬炒<br />\n港共立法會已經run唔倒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4d15a56919534f99de6c455b5f2301f2014067d","tid":2009161,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T14:19:49.000Z","msg":"民主黨一如以往賣香港"},{"pid":"e96b8f07bea6e25a74c0327e386a1f62f0e4573c","tid":2009161,"uid":64922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf3adcaf234a739a309aa701a0d7a469012af371","tid":2009161,"uid":64922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T14:17:27.000Z","msg":"過左35個唔駛講議案住<br />\n首先第一步大口狗個位就係民主派<br />\n主席個位已經可以玩殘港共<br />\n過35所有事務委員會正負又係包晒<br />\n基本唔撚駛玩咩否決權攬炒<br />\n港共立法會已經run唔倒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"